{
  "id": "6a2d2b1fc3c6e96eeb2a7ce8",
  "title": "如零",
  "created": 1781345058,
  "updated": 1781780313,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a2d2b1fc3c6e96eeb2a7ce8",
      "text": "如零",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781345058,
      "updated": 1781345058
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2d2afa0000000000bcfece",
      "text": " 「[ヌル]」（英：null）の[希哲館訳語][hiro.icon]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781345058,
      "updated": 1781345093
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2d2b870000000000bcfed2",
      "text": "  読み：にょれい",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781345199,
      "updated": 1781345202
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2d2bf70000000000bcfed5",
      "text": "  零の如し",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781345311,
      "updated": 1781345314
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2d2b1e0000000000bcfed0",
      "text": "  最近使う機会が減っていたが、[スイートポインタ]に関連して思い出した",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781345093,
      "updated": 1781345150
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2d2b560000000000bcfed1",
      "text": "  「ヌル」はプログラミング用語で一番嫌いなカタカナ英単語だった",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781345150,
      "updated": 1781345230
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2d2be10000000000bcfed4",
      "text": "   なんだこの気の抜けた語感は",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781345289,
      "updated": 1781345296
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2d94ed00000000005c24a4",
      "text": "    まんぜう軍で聞いたような[uminosachinomisokatsu.icon]",
      "userId": "69e3880c2d8712a4688ed0cf",
      "created": 1781372112,
      "updated": 1781780313
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2d2ba70000000000bcfed3",
      "text": "   これが原因でプログラミングが嫌いだった時期すらあったような",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781345231,
      "updated": 1781345277
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2d2e1b0000000000cccf56",
      "text": "   「如零」が出来た時は逆にかっこよすぎて笑った",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781345859,
      "updated": 1781346622
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2d2afb0000000000bcfecf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1781345059,
      "updated": 1781345059
    }
  ]
}